// InventoryModal.jsx
import React from 'react';
import {
    Dialog,
    DialogTitle,
    DialogContent,
    DialogActions,
    Button,
    TextField,
    MenuItem,
    Select,
    InputLabel,
    FormControl,
} from '@mui/material';

const InventoryModal = ({ isOpen, onClose }) => {
    return (
        <Dialog open={isOpen} onClose={onClose} maxWidth="sm" fullWidth>
            <DialogTitle>Add New Purchase Entry</DialogTitle>
            <DialogContent dividers>
                <TextField fullWidth label="Inventory Name" margin="normal" />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Category</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue="">
                        <MenuItem value="Fertilizer">Fertilizer</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Seeds">Seeds</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>

                <TextField fullWidth type="number" label="Price" margin="normal" />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Unit</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue="">
                        <MenuItem value="kg">kg</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="litre">litre</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>

                <TextField fullWidth label="Source" margin="normal" />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Source Company</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue="">
                        <MenuItem value="Company A">Company A</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Company B">Company B</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>

                <TextField fullWidth type="number" label="Available Quantity" margin="normal" />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Payment Status</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue="">
                        <MenuItem value="Paid">Paid</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Pending">Pending</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>
            </DialogContent>
            <DialogActions>
                <Button onClick={onClose} color="inherit">Cancel</Button>
                <Button variant="contained" onClick={onClose}>Save</Button>
            </DialogActions>
        </Dialog>
    );
};

export default InventoryModal;
